   "html": "1874 － 1965"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ よしざわ・けんきち ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n外相、仏印大使、台湾大使、駐華大使、外務省アジア局長兼欧米局長・政務局長、<a href=\"../p/ituyosi.html\">犬養毅</a>の女婿"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"08y.html\">一覧　（ヤ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E8%258A%25B3%25E6%25B2%25A2%2520%25E8%25AC%2599%25E5%2590%2589\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　新潟県出身。東京帝大卒業後、外務省入省。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　駐華公使として、カラハン駐華大使と交渉、日ソ基本条約を締結する。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　フランス大使を経て、国際連盟日本代表として、満州事変後の外交調整に携わる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1931/inu_1.html\">犬養内閣</a>の外相。貴族院勅選議員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　オランダ領東インド政府との経済交渉にあたるも不調に終わり、太平洋戦争を迎える。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、公職追放。解除後、台湾大使となり、その後も台湾擁護の立場に立つ。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
